    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the <strong>béchamel sauce</strong> from the heat</p><p>Tear your <strong>‘Nduja</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) into the<strong> béchamel sauce</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> and<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> to the pot and whisk everything together until well combined – this is your <strong>‘Nduja béchamel</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1666001225521-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1666001225521-x400.jpg",
