            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1666001225521-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Layer 1/3 of the<strong> green veggies </strong>over the bottom of an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong>, top with 1/3 of your <strong>lasagne sheets</strong>, being careful not to overlap the pasta, then top with 1/3<strong> </strong>of the <strong>‘Nduja béchamel</strong></p><p>Repeat this process until you end up with a final layer of<strong> 'Nduja béchamel</strong></p><p>Tip: You may need to layer differently depending on the size of your dish!</p><p>Top with the <strong>grated cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1666001227886-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
